title: Patriots reaction & Get my Lunch season preview
itunes:title: Patriots reaction & Get my Lunch season preview
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – discuss the latest reports involving the Patriots and give an update on Jason Pierre-Paul’s hand injury. The Heroes then preview the Patriots Steelers game before wrapping the show with the latest edition of “Go Get my Lunch!”
